<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link359434" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=359434&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F648216-alice-walker-uses-craft-moves-like-poor%2Fanswers%2F359434-it-is-a-wise-choice-as">flag</a>
</div>
