<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/578737-what-is-the-reason-behind-choosing-the">what is the reason behind choosing the color purple as atitle?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_578737'><a id="like_count_community_question_578737" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/578737?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">20 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F52892857-the-color-purple">like</a></span>

