        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/11486.The_Color_Purple">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1020619-educating-drew?shelf=ah-may-zing">ah-may-zing</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1020619-educating-drew?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1020619-educating-drew?shelf=sobs">sobs</a>, 
