    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3562307704" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3562307704" />
    <a title="Katie Lumsden" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8190907-katie-lumsden"><img alt="Katie Lumsden" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1607448164p2/8190907.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3562307704?book_show_action=true">Sep 30, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Katie Lumsden" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Katie Lumsden" href="/user/show/8190907-katie-lumsden">Katie Lumsden</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3562307704" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1395497227547283204">Well, that was amazing. I completely adore this, from the rich writing to the amazingly realised character development. It was just a joy to read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

